Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.19,0:00:04.98,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,First, you put everything \Nyou can think of into box A.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.52,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Then, you look and think about what is in there
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.52,0:00:12.36,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,and if you find any problems with something,\N you move it into box B.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.70,0:00:18.41,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,It's a way to figure out what you\N find "right" that a friend taught me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.04,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,There's something wrong about every single thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.87,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,You have to notice that first.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.21,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,After you learn both the good and bad sides,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.21,0:00:30.24,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,you can decide on what you find truly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Does that mean Kei isn't perfect either?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.72,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,I think so. Of course not.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.80,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Do you think he never makes mistakes?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.80,0:00:41.27,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,If so, that seems a bit like a tragedy.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.67,0:00:43.75,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,If he never makes mistakes,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.75,0:00:48.14,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,the moment he makes one,\N he'll stop being Asai Kei to you,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.27,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,which I find tragic.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.73,0:00:54.59,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to live knowing that\N I'm not allowed to make any mistakes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.97,0:01:00.32,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,You look like you're about to cry, Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.23,0:01:05.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I think I need to think more about certain things.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I don't know the bad sides of Asai Kei yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.45,0:01:10.77,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.64,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Let's think about it for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.34,0:01:19.72,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,You know, even I understand this.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.20,0:01:22.05,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,I'm human too, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.39,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Sacrificing a cat to save a human \Nmust be the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I think I'll be going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.62,0:01:33.98,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,I'll stay here for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.40,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.37,0:01:40.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Nonoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,It's not like we're stopping\N the cat's time for eternity.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.62,0:01:49.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Kei will eventually find a way to save\N everyone without sacrificing a cat.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.13,GJM_Main_1080p,No,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.87,0:02:05.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Are you with Nonoh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.95,0:02:08.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I was just about to go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,By the way, I want to ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire collapsed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I want to help her.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's Souma Sumire's condition?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's still asleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't know anything more.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Was she carried here at your request?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I asked Urachi to do that, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,You're quick to act.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Did you know this would happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.20,0:02:40.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I had my suspicions.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'll help her, just as planned.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I expected her to get hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,That's why I have to save her, just as planned.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.45,0:02:58.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Asai Kei, you're not that righteous.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,You're neither good nor pure.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.94,0:03:03.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you are a hero.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,You may not be omnipotent like you wish to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,You may be weak and reality might be cruel,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,but you are truly a hero\N even if you don't seem like one.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.60,0:03:16.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'm just doing as I please.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Asai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Putting in an effort for others\N sure seems to please you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Where's Haruki?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Heading this way as we speak.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,She really will do anything for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,This time she's helping me on one condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,She's really kind.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.76,0:03:38.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Demanding something in exchange means she\N understands the responsibility you're giving her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.20,0:03:43.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,It's always been like that—\NI owe everything to her help.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Eat some chocolate once \Nyou're done with everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Uka,0,0,0,,Chocolate works wonders when you're tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Hi, Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Good evening, Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I think Sakagami will be here any minute now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for asking this of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.40,0:04:06.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I don't think the condition you \Ngave me will be difficult with his help.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Why do you want this, though?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Because I want to understand you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.22,0:04:15.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,If you really aren't perfect,\N I want to learn about it and try to understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'm not perfect at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.18,0:04:22.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,But I don't know your bad sides.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.06,0:04:27.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I think that until now, \NI've never really tried to understand you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.37,0:04:32.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Somewhere deep in my heart,\N I've been wishing for you to never change.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.17,0:04:38.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Kei, I've been afraid that my love for you\N was blinding me to who you really are.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kei?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.10,0:04:45.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,This is the second time you've said you loved me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,When was the first?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You're going to remember that day in a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Sa,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Let's start, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}So these are Kei's memories...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}How kind yet cruel they are...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}How clever yet foolish he is...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.83,0:05:22.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}How bold yet sensitive he is...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asai Kei is very special to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}This equilibrium he maintains is perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.25,0:05:33.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so beautiful and peaceful.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I love you.{ep 02 line 340}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Are you happy?{ep 02 line 351}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I don't know.{ep 02 line 352}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.71,0:05:54.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I found one of the mistakes you made.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.56,0:06:02.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Two years ago, when you kissed me \Non the rooftop of the south school building,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.37,0:06:06.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I was actually happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I sure took the long, cowardly way around.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I did the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Tyl,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sumire, dear?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Tyl,0,0,0,,You look awfully sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Say, Tyltyl.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Will you listen to my request?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Tyl,0,0,0,,Of course. Whatever it may be.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.53,0:06:47.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Then make me the same as you, Tyltyl.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.45,0:06:52.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Make me able to do anything, like you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.48,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Yes, it certainly has.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.50,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be visiting me more.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.50,0:07:12.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of effort to get here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'll try to keep that in mind, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.28,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,I don't mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.70,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,But please do try to visit more.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,By the way, have you seen Souma Sumire?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.04,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,Me? No.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.77,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,Tyltyl met with her, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.00,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,Are you saving her this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.09,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,What are you, some kind of a hero?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,No, I'm Souma Sumire's friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.53,0:07:39.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Souma is the second most important person to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.23,0:07:43.98,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,In such a ranking, only first place matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.98,0:07:48.07,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,She's sitting alone in a corner precisely \Nbecause second place means nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,That might be true.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.26,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,Are you going to make her first?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'm going to get her to make do with being second.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.91,GJM_Main_1080p,My,0,0,0,,You're so cruel.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I am cruel and selfish.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,She's here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,The rooftop of the south school \Nbuilding, the tetrapods...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Both are important places,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,but to the Souma from two years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Not the current one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.67,0:08:22.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Once we're done with everything, \Nlet's have a Kit Kat together.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.89,0:08:25.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Take a break with some chocolate
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,and plan to make some curry together.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,We'll make the best curry in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Haruki, save.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Save.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,It's 7:15:20 PM.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.96,0:09:04.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,This is my apartment. Of course I'd come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You didn't have to come all the way\N to the dream world for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I will be the one to define your happiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I don't think I can save you.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,But you can save me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You can make me happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I've hurt you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,That's only what you think.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.67,0:09:35.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You've been a greater help to me than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.40,0:09:41.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,The happiness you ensured for me is true happiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.66,0:09:45.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I really am happy.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Thank you.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.39,0:09:50.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,So please, keep helping me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I can keep being happy thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It's too bright.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You're always the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And that's so unbearably painful for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I knew it. You're crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Look at my future.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.84,0:10:29.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,In one month, in half a year, in a year...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.87,0:10:33.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Whenever I see you, you're smiling.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Look at that future.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If that's what you wish for, \NI'm sure that's how it'll be.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.38,0:10:44.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,But I'm scared of such a future.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Knowing that I can't have you for myself
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,and I keep smiling despite that\N is such a scary thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,But fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If you accept my one condition,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Play a game with me.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll do what you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,And if you win?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If I win, let me decide your future for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You'll become mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And you'll live here in this dream world.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,We'll live here together
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.70,0:11:23.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,like two pebbles, never causing any trouble for anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Sure. What kind of game will we play?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.69,0:11:32.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You haven't said my name even once since entering this room.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're being considerate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Please, Kei. Say my name.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.12,0:11:46.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If you say it right, you win.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Good evening, Haruki.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Took you a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thirty minutes have passed...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Have you met with Kei?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Yeah, we talked.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,In my hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Kei made a promise with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.29,0:12:18.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,We played a game, and he'd become mine if he lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And he did lose.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,That's why he's like this now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I'm practically the same as Tyltyl now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Turning him into a pebble is no big deal for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,There is no way you'd wish for such a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If I really were Souma Sumire, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,That's so stupid!{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If that pebble isn't Asai Kei,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,there's no need to be panicking that much, is there?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.73,0:12:53.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Haruki Misora, that really is him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,He can't see or hear anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,but keeps thinking inside there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It's a pebble which possesses his consciousness.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, give up.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,He's already mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for not mincing words.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.16,0:13:16.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,To think Haruki Misora has become so human...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Two years is quite a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Whatever,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.72,0:13:23.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,there's no need to be considerate of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.71,0:13:25.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,This is absolutely ridiculous.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You can't claim Asai Kei as yours\N just because you've done this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.54,0:13:36.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You let me into this room exactly \Nbecause you're perfectly aware of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You're like a child throwing a tantrum.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You cannot be satisfied with such an outcome,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,so you're trying to truly claim \NAsai Kei for yourself now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.09,0:13:49.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Basically, you've been waiting for me \Nto come and let you have him, no?{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I see, that's such an effective method.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I was always on his side,\N I even threw my life away for him,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,so if I got depressed after all that,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,he wouldn't be himself if he left me alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And if I turned him into a pebble,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.81,0:14:08.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,there was no way you wouldn't \Ncome to save him, Haruki Misora.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You put him way above yourself,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.02,0:14:16.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,so you're even able to leave\N his side if it's for his sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And if that's the case...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.26,0:14:21.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Give Asai Kei to me.{PV}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.72,0:14:29.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I used to be able to use my ability by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I could until the summer two years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,But after one of my resets
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.00,0:14:37.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire died, even though she didn't before.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,And so Asai Kei was hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.89,0:14:44.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,That's when I became unable\N to use my ability on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I didn't want the same thing to happen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,He's the only one.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.92,0:14:53.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,He's the only person who remembers what happens \Nbefore resets, and I didn't want him to get hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.24,0:15:01.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,No, I was scared that if I used my ability \Non my own and failed, he'd hate me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.09,0:15:04.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Can you use your reset without him now?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.06,0:15:07.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Rese—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.07,0:15:25.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You really do care only about him, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.51,0:15:37.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,There's no way I could've \Nmissed that future, could I?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.19,0:15:42.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd just give him to me\N after spending two years with him, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.52,0:15:47.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,There's no way Kei wouldn't \Nsee through such a plan, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.15,0:15:52.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It's not like I can calculate \Nevery single thing to go my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It's not like I can help having \Nfeelings like everyone else!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.74,0:16:05.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,There's no point if you can't be fooled.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.61,0:16:10.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,So I was right that you\N wouldn't turn Kei into a pebble.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You did this for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You did this so that I could \Nuse my ability by myself again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,That's the only reason you lied.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It wasn't for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.45,0:16:25.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Kei is trying to shoulder the responsibility\N for all the abilities in Sakurada.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.67,0:16:29.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You can't stay in his care forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,You, if no one else,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.10,0:16:35.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,have to be his savior while he tries\N to save everyone and everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If you can't take responsibility for your own ability,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I don't want you to stay by his side.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I could say exactly the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Do you know what my dream is?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,To be by Kei's side.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,He's smart, he has an excellent ability,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,so I want to be able to be useful to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,That's my dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I want to be like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Haruki Misora,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.81,0:17:17.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I wanted to be like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.05,0:17:21.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll become able to stay\N useful by his side, just like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,And when I can fulfill both my and your role,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,my selfish self will be satisfied.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,What a cheap provocation.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,He actually asked me just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,He wants me to keep helping him, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.52,0:17:39.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And when it comes to working together\N for him, I'm the more capable one,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,so I don't think I should let you \Ntake this role from me as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Where's Kei?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Already awake.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.18,0:17:52.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Let's go back too, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Please, Kei. Say my name.{line 207}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.16,0:18:08.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If you say it right, you win.{line 208}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You were Souma Sumire the whole time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.65,0:18:25.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,The message sent by Tomoki's ability\N reached you too, didn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.21,0:18:29.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,How were you able to believe that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I just had to think about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.96,0:18:38.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,{\q2}If the message didn't reach you, you would've been\N too kind to say that whichever I chose was true.{referring to: ep 10 lines 362-365}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,But Kei,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.10,0:18:45.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to believe anything\N until you decided for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I knew that even if I heard my message,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.14,0:18:51.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to believe that I'm Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.15,0:18:55.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,The reason I was able to plan everything
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,was because I knew my own weaknesses.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.96,0:19:03.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I tried to make you decide \Nmy own name, my own identity.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.08,0:19:10.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I made you carry another burden.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Souma.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.46,0:19:15.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You might not know about this,\N but I'm actually very stubborn.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.49,0:19:20.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Two years ago, \NI decided that I'd bring you back to life,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,and since then I've been prepared\N to carry all kinds of burdens.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.49,0:19:29.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,But there's times when it's too heavy,\N and you just want to run away from it all, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.24,0:19:33.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,If it's too heavy, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I have my ability so that\N I wouldn't just abandon all of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.14,0:19:41.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,What I wished for was to move forward\N without throwing burdens away.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Morning, Souma.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Did you look at my face while I was asleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Is that bad? You looked pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I don't really care,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,but even I haven't seen it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.97,0:20:10.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Why were you with me, not Haruki?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,There's two reasons.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.19,0:20:16.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,One is that I felt like you'd be the first to wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,And the other one?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.88,0:20:20.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,The moon is beautiful.{no. no. NO. NOOO. I DON'T ACCEPT THIS ANIME ENDING LIKE THIS. I REFUSE.}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Huh?{JUST LOOK AT HER FAAAACEEEEE}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.56,0:20:25.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You were sleeping by the window, and Haruki wasn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I've lied to you once.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.69,0:20:38.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,What was it about?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I actually hate messages.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Please listen to my voice in person from now on, Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I definitely will.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.44,0:20:56.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,It'd be kind of awkward to see Haruki Misora now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,If I wander around,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,I'm sure Urachi will come to pick me up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on your help again, Souma.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Sou,0,0,0,,Always, Kei.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Has she left?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.89,0:21:24.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Why were you hiding?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.64,0:21:28.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,It'd be kind of embarrassing to see Souma Sumire.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.60,0:21:32.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Do you want me to be friends with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.76,0:21:36.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,It's not like you wish for her to be unhappy, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You'd help her if she was in need.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.84,0:21:40.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,If I could.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Then that's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.35,0:21:47.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know what to do if \Nyou told me to be friends with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.26,0:21:50.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,You dislike her that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.76,0:21:55.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm fine with me and Souma\N competing properly as rivals.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'd say that's... more natural.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.60,0:21:58.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm sure you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.09,0:22:06.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Kei, does this mean everything's over now?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,For now, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Let's make dinner together, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.36,0:22:11.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,We'll go shopping tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.12,0:22:15.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I also have an idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.57,0:22:16.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.82,0:22:19.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of growing my hair out a bit.{Hell yes. -Pik}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,That's great, but why?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.74,0:22:23.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,I remembered today.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.93,0:22:27.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,You told me a long time ago\N that my hair was pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.33,0:22:29.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Ha,0,0,0,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.45,0:22:31.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.48,0:22:35.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Kei,0,0,0,,My memory is pretty good.
Comment: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.80,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}On such a cold dark sky of grey
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.75,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}Rises the sun, which breathes life into it
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.17,0:18:40.05,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}A scenery so plain and so mundane
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.39,0:18:49.65,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}And yet it seems to break my heart, it's so dear to me
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.60,0:18:54.19,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}As the time never stops passing by
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.57,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}You get lost while searching for
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.49,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}Pure like the rays of a morning star
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.45,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}What we all yearn for the most
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.91,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}In what colors bliss is dyed
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.46,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}Struggling against all your past mistakes
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.67,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}At last from the answer you found kindness fills your heart
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.63,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}More beautiful than anything you know
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.47,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}And you find it behind a dark veil of sadness
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.80,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}If I closed my eyes and stopped my thoughts
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.60,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}If it were so simple to just
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.52,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}Lock your own heart
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.81,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}How lovely life would be
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.81,0:19:34.90,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}But I believe you have the key
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.69,0:19:41.15,SagradaED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,200)\3c&H65220B&\be3}To let my soul be free
Comment: 5,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.52,0:22:20.02,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}I used to say there was a novel I loved
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.02,0:22:23.53,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}That I kept on a shelf and never opened up
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.53,0:22:26.86,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}"See, this is how you stay true to yourself"
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.86,0:22:29.41,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}Showing off, proud of just being me
Dialogue: 5,0:22:29.41,0:22:30.49,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}People around me
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.49,0:22:33.74,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}Try to sound mature and take some wise words
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.12,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}They use them as if those words belonged to them
Dialogue: 5,0:22:37.12,0:22:40.13,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}Showing off the fake wisdom they had stolen
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.13,0:22:43.13,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}So I laughed at them
Dialogue: 5,0:22:43.13,0:22:47.39,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}But actually my sense of self that I kept on a shelf
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.84,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}Was no different from what I'd been laughing at
Dialogue: 5,0:22:50.84,0:22:53.81,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}And the truth is that I already knew
Dialogue: 5,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.89,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}But no more lies, it's time
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.89,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}For my heart's reset
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.89,0:23:01.10,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}I'll be the one to let go of myself
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.10,0:23:04.61,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}So I told myself somewhere deep down in my heart
Dialogue: 5,0:23:04.61,0:23:07.65,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}Even if they might talk behind my back
Dialogue: 5,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.28,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}Why should I care when I don't turn around?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.28,0:23:11.62,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}You can choose
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.62,0:23:14.78,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}To follow the path someone's already walked
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.78,0:23:18.25,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}But wouldn't you rather leave footprints yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.25,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}You believed your own dreams and chose a path
Dialogue: 5,0:23:21.25,0:23:24.25,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}So it's the right one, just trust in your heart
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.25,0:23:26.63,Sagrada-OP,,0,0,40,karaoke,{\fad(120,120)\an9\bord6\3c&H000000&\be1\b1}It'll all be fine
